DocAttribute.Name: Tag
DocAttribute.Documentation: The tag (or label) identifier at the particular instance of a product, e.g. the serial number, or the position number. It is the identifier at the occurrence level.

DocAttribute.Name: FillsVoids
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to the Fills Relationship that puts the Element into the Opening within another Element.

DocAttribute.Name: ConnectedTo
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to the element connection relationship. The relationship then refers to the other element to which this element is connected to.

DocAttribute.Name: HasCoverings
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to _IfcCovering_ by virtue of the objectified relationship _IfcRelCoversBldgElement_. It defines the concept of an element having coverings attached.

DocAttribute.Name: HasProjections
DocAttribute.Documentation: Projection relationship that adds a feature (using a Boolean union) to the _IfcBuildingElement_.

DocAttribute.Name: ReferencedInStructures
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference relationship to the spatial structure element, to which the element is additionally associated. > <font color="#ff0000"><small> IFC2x Edition 3 CHANGE  The inverse attribute has been added with upward compatibility for file based exchange. <small></small></small></font>

DocAttribute.Name: HasPorts
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to the element to port connection relationship. The relationship then refers to the port which is contained in this element.

DocAttribute.Name: HasOpenings
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to the Voids Relationship that creates an opening in an element. An element can incorporate zero-to-many openings.

DocAttribute.Name: IsConnectionRealization
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to the connection relationship with realizing element. The relationship then refers to the realizing element which provides the physical manifestation of the connection relationship.

DocAttribute.Name: ProvidesBoundaries
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to Space Boundaries by virtue of the objectified relationship IfcRelSeparatesSpaces. It defines the concept of an Building Element bounding Spaces.

DocAttribute.Name: ConnectedFrom
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to the element connection relationship. The relationship then refers to the other element that is connected to this element.

DocAttribute.Name: ContainedInStructure
DocAttribute.Documentation: Containment relationship to the spatial structure element, to which the element is primarily associated.
